beer.beer_description:
Deep and rich like Newtown’s history, our seventh birthday celebratory ale pours with a
long lasting, off white head. A complex spice and berry aroma plays across the strong, malty
undertones which linger long on the palate, first with sweetness which quickly becomes refreshing
bitterness. Best enjoyed with mates, straight from the bottle at sunset in Camperdown Park.

beer.beer_name: Double Dry Hopped Envie w/ Galaxy

beer.beer_description: Newtowner is a 4.8% beer in the style of a new Aussie pale ale made with Australian Pale and Crystal malts. It is finished with a trio of Australian hops, producing a golden, refreshing beer with a well-rounded malt and hop balance and a slightly dry finish. Perfect for Newtowners to enjoy this summer.
